commentaries.commentary: Ibrahimović takes the pass! Chests it! Overhead bicycle kick from 25 yards! OH MY WORD! UNBELIEVABLE! ZLATAN! WHAT A GOAL! Absolute screamer! Top corner! Sweden leads 4-2! He's celebrating, shirt off! Teammates rush in! Pure ecstasy!
commentaries.speaker: COMMENTATOR_1

commentaries.commentary: That is an absolutely extraordinary moment of pure brilliance from Ibrahimović! The audacity to even attempt such a bicycle kick, coupled with the impeccable technical execution from that distance, is simply astounding. This goal will be replayed for decades, a truly iconic masterpiece.
commentaries.speaker: COMMENTATOR_2

commentaries.commentary: You're absolutely right, an iconic goal from Ibrahimović! And the action has been relentless ever since! OH! What a save! The goalkeeper, diving to his right, just deflects it onto the crossbar! Player number 5 was certain it was in! Huddleston was there for the follow-up, but the danger is gone! What incredible defending!
commentaries.speaker: COMMENTATOR_1
